import React from 'react'
import {Grid,Typography,makeStyles, StylesProvider} from '@material-ui/core'
import Posttemplate from './Posttemplate'



function Posts() {
    
    return (
       
          <Grid item lg={3} sm={4} xs={12}>
            <Posttemplate/>
            <Posttemplate/>
            <Posttemplate/>
            <Posttemplate/>
            <Posttemplate/>
          </Grid>
        
    )
}

export default Posts
